By: Chang Po-tuan
---
Get one (grain of tan, medicine) and you will be sufficient for thousands (of
affairs). Do not make distinction between south, north, west and east. Fail
and fail again; but build upon your previous achievements. The valuable
things of life should not be toyed with.
